These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, iced-tea, juice, milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, martial-arts, superhero, horror, documentary
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, thai, american, spanish, canadian
5 different pets are kept: snake, pony, mouse, fish, goat
 1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the owner of the snake is the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the dutch is on the left of the american##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person drinking milk is between the thai and the person watching documentary movies##2
12. the spanish is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
13. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | water        | mirinda | milk     | iced-tea   | juice |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | martial-arts      | horror | documentary   | drama    |
| Nationality   | spanish  | thai     | dutch | american | canadian  |
| Pet           | pony | mouse      | goat     | fish   | snake     |

