.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, drawing, card-games, traveling, video-games
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, classical, gospel, dubstep, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, pakistani, japanese, colombian, nigerian
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, ship, bus, train, motorbike
 1. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the person driving the ship is between the thai and the fan of rock##2
 6. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the fan of indie is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the japanese is the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of classical##1
11. the japanese is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the person driving the ship is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | traveling | filmmaking | video-games    | drawing  | card-games    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | classical       | gospel      | indie | dubstep        |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | pakistani     | thai    | colombian  | japanese     |
| Transport     | bus    | ship | motorbike | train | trike |

