.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, hiking, card-games, traveling, camping
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, drama, scientific, animation, fantasy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, house, salsa, r&b
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, surfing, snowboarding, baseball, climbing
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is the fan of folk##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the fan of house is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | writing | camping     | card-games   | hiking   | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | drama | action | animation | scientific        |
| Music-Genre   | house      | folk      | salsa       | r&b       | hip-hop       |
| Sport         | surfing | climbing  | baseball    | weightlifting    | snowboarding        |

