.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, cucumber, pear, lettuce, grapefruit
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, dancing, trance-climbing, camping, collecting
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, metal, gospel, trance
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian, australian, spanish, mexican
 1. the brazilian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the mexican is between the fan of gospel and the person eating lettuce##2
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is trance-climbing##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the right of the australian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is trance-climbing is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of d&b##1
 9. the fan of trance is in the middle##1
10. the fan of gospel is the nigerian##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is trance-climbing##1
12. the nigerian is on the right of the fan of metal##1
13. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | grapefruit  | pear     | lettuce   | cucumber     | blueberry |
| Hobby         | collecting | sudoku    | trance-climbing  | camping | dancing   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | country    | trance     | metal     | gospel    |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | australian | spanish | mexican | nigerian   |

