.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, 7up, fanta
There 5 different types of food: grapes, nectarine, onion, peas, carrot
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, scientist, project-manager, teacher, firefighter
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, sailing, skiing, cycling, lacrosse
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the bartender##1
 2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person eating grapes##2
 5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the scientist##1
 8. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating onion##1
12. the teacher is on the left of the bartender##1
13. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | 7up       | fanta       | iced-tea   | sprite      | hot-chocolate    |
| Food       | carrot | peas        | grapes       | onion       | nectarine |
| Job        | firefighter     | scientist        | teacher | bartender        | project-manager  |
| Sport      | cycling | skiing | baseball      | lacrosse | sailing  |

