 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person drinking cola is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is the malaysian##1
 8. the british is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the right of the chinese##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the dutch##1
13. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
