 2. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the spanish##2
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
 7. the american is on the right of the australian##1
 8. the canadian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the fish is the american##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person driving the van##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the right of the australian##1
12. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
