 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the boat is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate       | tea    | water | sprite  | cola        |
| Hobby       | gardening | writing | cooking  | fishing | puzzles    |
| Sport       | biathlon        | baseball   | climbing  | surfing   | skiing |
| Transport   | helicopter       | boat      | tram      | jet-ski | subway  |

