.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea, lemonade
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, scientist, software-developer, doctor, dancer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, horror, family, zombie
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, r&b, rock, classical, folk
 1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the doctor is between the person watching horror movies and the software-developer##2
 3. the person drinking tea is the doctor##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the dancer and the fan of r&b##2
 7. the fan of classical is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is the fan of rock##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the left of the dancer##1
10. the police-officer is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
11. the software-developer is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
