 2. the thai is on the left of the german##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the fish is between the mexican and the owner of the rat##2
 6. the mexican is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person driving the subway and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is boatd-games##2
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's hobby is boatd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is boatd-games is on the right of the chinese##1

