.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, filmmaking, singing, salsa-climbing, collecting
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, sports, adventure, family, disaster
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, jazz, disco, metal, salsa
There are 5 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, colombian, indian, spanish
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is between the indian and the fan of salsa##2
 3. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of house##1
 5. the fan of house is between the spanish and the fan of disco##2
 6. the spanish is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is the fan of metal##1
 8. the person who's hobby is salsa-climbing is the fan of jazz##1
 9. the pakistani is the fan of jazz##1
10. the person who's hobby is salsa-climbing is on the right of the colombian##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | singing    | collecting  | filmmaking  | writing      | salsa-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | disaster   | family | adventure | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | house    | salsa    | metal       | jazz         |
| Nationality   | indian  | japanese | spanish    | colombian     | pakistani      |

 